songs.title: Beat It On Down The Line

comments:
First set timed from an AUD, second set from a worthless SBD with the following cuts and splices: Estimated cuts off and seems to restart with the opening notes of He's Gone which has a splice of its own. A segment of the Drums has been cut out. A minor splice appears in the Other one. and finally, Good Lovin' cuts off. If that's not enough for you, the first set SBD has a minor (about 11 secs) splice in Bird Song and the first 30 seconds or so is missing from I Know You Rider. Some people should not be allowed near tapes.

*Satisfaction timing provided by Paul Gibian
